<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>아이디 찾기 - ECO-LIFE Mall</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root { --primary-color: #064E3B; --primary-hover: #064E3B; --bg-color: #f8fafc; --text-dark: #1e293b; --text-gray: #64748b; }
        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: 'Noto Sans KR', sans-serif; }
        body { background-color: var(--bg-color); display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; min-height: 100vh; }
        .login-container { background: white; width: 100%; max-width: 400px; padding: 40px; border-radius: 20px; box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05); text-align: center; }
        .back-to-home { display: inline-block; margin-bottom: 20px; color: var(--text-gray); text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9em; transition: 0.2s; }
        .back-to-home:hover { color: var(--primary-color); }
        h2 { color: var(--text-dark); font-size: 1.8rem; margin-bottom: 30px; font-weight: 700; }
        .input-group { text-align: left; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .input-group label { display: block; font-size: 0.85em; color: var(--text-gray); margin-bottom: 8px; margin-left: 4px; }
        input { width: 100%; padding: 14px 18px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0; border-radius: 12px; font-size: 1rem; background-color: #f1f5f9; transition: all 0.2s; }
        input:focus { outline: none; border-color: var(--primary-color); background-color: white; box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.1); }
        button { width: 100%; background-color: var(--primary-color); color: white; padding: 16px; border: none; border-radius: 12px; cursor: pointer; font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 700; margin-top: 10px; transition: all 0.2s; }
        button:hover { background-color: var(--primary-hover); transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.3); }
        .find-links { margin-top: 25px; display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 15px; }
        .find-links a { font-size: 0.85em; color: var(--text-gray); text-decoration: none; transition: 0.2s; }
        .find-links a:hover { color: var(--primary-color); }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="login-container">
        <a href="../login" class="back-to-home">👈 로그인으로 돌아가기</a>
        <h2>아이디 찾기</h2>
        
        <form action="./find-id" method="post">
            <div class="input-group">
                <label>이름</label>
                <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="가입 시 입력한 이름" required>
            </div>
            <div class="input-group">
                <label>연락처</label>
                <input type="text" name="phone" placeholder="예: 010-1234-5678" required>
            </div>
            <button type="submit">아이디 확인</button>
        </form>
        <div class="find-links">
            <a href="./find-pw">비밀번호가 기억나지 않으시나요?</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>